{"tid":1085905,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽馬] 競賽小組嘅公平一致性喺邊?","createTime":"2019-03-31T13:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T18:51:44.000Z","uid":44445,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c1c36d6d4ddc2d128c8825d7939819ea585f42","tid":1085905,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"3月17日 田草4班1600米 贏馬神器<br />\n<br />\n賴維銘被指控違反賽事規例第99（2）條，即<span style=\"color: red;\">每匹馬的騎師均須於整場賽事中採取一切合理而又可容許的措施，確保給予其座騎十足爭勝機會，或取得最佳名次。</span><br />\n<br />\n3月31日 田草3班1200米 太陽威威<br />\n<br />\n騎師潘頓喺末段嘅積極性同同日第9場嘅精益求精相比<br />\n大家可以睇吓係有咩分別，小弟不予置評<br />\n結果太陽威威喺潘頓策騎下失三甲，只得第四<br />\n競賽小組不但冇採取任何對賴維銘相同嘅手法去處理，喺賽後報告連警戒，甚至提醒都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個賽後報告關於太陽威威嘅只得一句：<br />\n過了八百米處後，「太陽威威」在沒有遮擋下走外疊。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁嘅競賽小組好難令人信服係公平公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d31b2ba8581498a906a8e11e2fc6e3444a9502","tid":1085905,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de4b6992f008fee6ab167b7a8dd35579a34b17b","tid":1085905,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6d31b2ba8581498a906a8e11e2fc6e3444a9502","tid":1085905,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"賴維銘個場小組on9抽秤"},{"pid":"a73adfdbba96586200077e62b43b90cccda8e714","tid":1085905,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T15:59:15.000Z","msg":"係人都知潘狗係馬會契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5bd0d2ecd7fb3cf128ec99f8d900dcf2d75b52","tid":1085905,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"冇 唯有戒賭<br />\n俾條撚樣玩死<br />\n四個第四 